                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060917-41-defend322 t18060917-41-punish223"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 30.</p>
               <p>London Jury, before Mr. Justice Le Blanc.</p>
